{"tid":96684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎分享下] 香港地好人好事","createTime":"2017-01-27T04:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T05:54:50.000Z","uid":70484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6108d2674ccab497920356bf08595318fa36c14","tid":96684,"uid":70484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:50:56.000Z","msg":"有路人經過提我巴士站轉左停車位<br />\n叫我去前少少排先上到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有有個呀叔見到我唔夠銀坐小巴<br />\n主動幫我唱錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝你地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794402d51712f3d725bef50b16b1fcf6a46cfddb","tid":96684,"uid":27196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"提我個背囊未拉好拉鍊"},{"pid":"cb854ff0c2c8bb0b5fa2d647f660699e25fa9eb8","tid":96684,"uid":71883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:04:51.000Z","msg":"我幫人：<br />\n有日唔記得帶八達通，諗住去買飛，突然有個中學生埋黎問可唔可以借十蚊比佢搭車，我見到佢係我間母校，跟住就好型咁係褲袋比左張廿蚊佢。(其實係我無十蚊紙)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85bdf2788855122d67dd559e70557af6fb2333b8","tid":96684,"uid":70484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幫人：<br />\n有日唔記得帶八達通，諗住去買飛，突然有個中學生埋黎問可唔可以借十蚊比佢搭車，我見到佢係我間母校，跟住就好型咁係褲袋比左張廿蚊佢。(其實係我無十蚊紙)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下次問巴打借錢買飛先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1dde24c89c8e693070d96c5ed561df6f3902a9d","tid":96684,"uid":3627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"讀書果陣，連續一兩個月每晚訓得三四個鐘，然後再通左兩晚宵趕project。<br />\n<br />\n之後果日放學，繁忙時間搭西鐵，逼到人貼人，我就挨係到訓著左，架車chok左下我成個人撞左落個啊姨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係朦朧間好似同左佢講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知佢冇怪我不突止，仲要見到有人起身落車果陣幫我霸住個位叫我坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我坐低之後，其實我果刻已經清醒晒，但我唔敢抬頭，扮訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係果一刻太感動流左兩行馬尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多謝你啊姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係你令我知道香港人仲係有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 從此我搭車果陣見到有學生/上班族企係到訓，而我唔需要坐，都會讓座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef938afcf619ebabfd37521861ae9770ea7d096","tid":96684,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"一對情侶唔讓座比廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n難能可貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5cb5c3f2328026cb5017f9ae2b1a6eb03c604d","tid":96684,"uid":70484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0